channel.title: Props to the Coders
channel.description: Honestly with the recent update my game’s FPS range changed drastically. During the day I can have at minimum 16 frames per second but at night my computer’s frames per second drastically increases to at most 34 and stays constant at 32. I don’t know what caused the drastic increase in frames, but keep up the good work
